HP revised their advisory to include details about HP-UX 11.04 (VVOS).  This issue affects HP-UX 11.04 (VVOS) with Virtualvault A.04.50 or Virtualvault A.04.60 or Virtualvault A.04.70 installed.  These platforms are only affected if Java has been downloaded and integrated on Virtualvault.
